message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question generation, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
